Content:









``polars horizontal``
[link: /commands/categories/expression.md] ’Щ@59fde2cc813ad38e843e1e39075095fd9c2e353cb9f45b9e14a7518451dce627ЩhTitle: title: polars horizontal
Path: Signature
Content:
``> polars horizontal {flags} (type) ...rest``
’Щ@36d3ba3696689b3f972308b3e10ba379c503401d5f8259d3c065544f154a6576ЩҒTitle: title: polars horizontal
Path: Flags
Content:
``--nulls, -n``
: If set, null value in the input will lead to null output.
’Щ@a797f1d47f8b0fc69a1fb6511b912541618661cbe587fe208a669797e9635995ЩРTitle: title: polars horizontal
Path: Parameters
Content:
``type``
: Horizontal operation. Values of all, any, min, max, sum, and mean are accepted.
``...rest``
: Expression(s) that define the lazy group-by.
’Щ@ded088213bcb0235658ac69838807946fe0bca0e8353a31e41a49eab29035748ЩfTitle: title: polars horizontal
Path: Input/output types:
Content:
input
output
any
polars_expression
’Щ@63387f0bdc4ccc6564ecb8abbc357b7178dd0dcaa73ffec77ac38af06281e755Ъ	Title: title: polars horizontal
Path: Examples
Content:
Horizontal sum across two columns (ignore nulls by default)
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[a b]; [1 2] [2 3] [3 4] [4 5] [5 null]]
                    | polars into-df
                    | polars select (polars horizontal sum a b)
                    | polars collect
в•ӯв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв•®
в”Ӯ # в”Ӯ sum в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө
в”Ӯ 0 в”Ӯ   3 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 1 в”Ӯ   5 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 2 в”Ӯ   7 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 3 в”Ӯ   9 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 4 в”Ӯ   5 в”Ӯ
в•°в”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв•Ҝ


```
Horizontal sum across two columns while accounting for nulls
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[a b]; [1 2] [2 3] [3 4] [4 5] [5 null]]
                    | polars into-df
                    | polars select (polars horizontal sum a b --nulls)
                    | polars collect
в•ӯв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв•®
в”Ӯ # в”Ӯ sum в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө
в”Ӯ 0 в”Ӯ   3 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 1 в”Ӯ   5 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 2 в”Ӯ   7 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 3 в”Ӯ   9 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 4 в”Ӯ     в”Ӯ
в•°в”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв•Ҝ


```
